tell you which way to go,

00:04:02.970 --> 00:04:04.682
but it's not going to turn
your car for you.

00:04:04.682 --> 00:04:06.540
If your heart's telling
you to turn left,

00:04:06.540 --> 00:04:07.400
you better turn left.

00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:10.739
And there are a lot of people
who wait too late to listen to

00:04:10.739 --> 00:04:11.989
their heart.

00:04:14.555 --> 00:04:16.350
-Every single person
has a story.

00:04:16.350 --> 00:04:19.120
