But no one ever knows what's
going to be coming up ahead.

00:04:25.690 --> 00:04:26.920
And it could change
everything.

00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:29.910
And it could be better than
you even expected it.

00:04:29.910 --> 00:04:32.090
-I just can't wait to see
what the next few

00:04:32.090 --> 00:04:33.340
weeks have in store.

