00:53:04.150 --> 00:53:07.220
And there's more compromise
that each of us, as

00:53:07.220 --> 00:53:09.270
individuals, have to take
in certain situations.

00:53:09.270 --> 00:53:12.370
But those fundamental questions,
of who am I and

00:53:12.370 --> 00:53:15.550
what's important to me and do
I make these decisions for

00:53:15.550 --> 00:53:20.860
myself or for other people, I
