00:53:39.460 --> 00:53:41.620
of something bigger, that was
sustainable, that had a

00:53:41.620 --> 00:53:44.220
lasting impression, that had
a lasting footprint.

00:53:44.220 --> 00:53:45.860
And I think that was something
